&lt;h2>Verification — what the reviewer looks for&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="verification--what-the-reviewer-looks-for">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#verification--what-the-reviewer-looks-for" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Lockfile and manifest pin &lt;code>marimo&lt;/code> to &lt;code>&amp;gt;=0.23.0&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>No vulnerable marimo version remains in dependency tree.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Tests/lint are green or failures are clearly pre-existing.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>PR includes runtime hardening follow-ups if service was internet-reachable.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
